<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 03:12:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亚洲股市稳定；日经指数因日本央行的关键押注而受损</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-14/</link><description>亚洲股市周四维持在七个月高位附近，但主要横盘整理，因为投资者等待新的催化剂，这将进一步明确全球利率宽松周期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 03:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>经中国批准，日本建投公司将于 3 月 19 日开始对 JSR 进行要约收购 - 彭博社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/japans-jic-start-tender-offer-jsr-march-19-after-chinese-approval-bloomberg-news-2024-03-14/</link><description>据彭博社周四报道，日本国家投资公司（JIC）在获得中国监管机构批准后，将于 3 月 19 日开始对芯片材料制造商 JSR Corp 的股票进行要约收购。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 02:56:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/japans-jic-start-tender-offer-jsr-march-19-after-chinese-approval-bloomberg-news-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>尽管地区局势紧张，越南武器进口仍减少</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-arms-imports-drop-trickle-despite-regional-tensions-2024-03-14/</link><description>周一公布的数据显示，越南去年的武器进口放缓，因为越南致力于将供应多样化，远离俄罗斯，而专家警告说，该国在地区冲突中可能很脆弱。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 02:37:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-arms-imports-drop-trickle-despite-regional-tensions-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国炸鸡店爆炸造成7人死亡27人受伤调查开始</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/probe-begins-after-7-killed-27-injured-fried-chicken-shop-explosion-china-2024-03-14/</link><description>北京附近的中国三河县当地政府官员周四表示，他们已开始调查一家炸鸡店发生大规模爆炸的原因，爆炸造成 7 人死亡、27 人受伤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 02:09:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/probe-begins-after-7-killed-27-injured-fried-chicken-shop-explosion-china-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国库存数据和俄罗斯炼油厂遇袭支撑油价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-underpinned-by-us-inventory-data-attacks-russian-refineries-2024-03-14/</link><description>美国原油库存意外下降表明需求走强，周四亚洲贸易中油价延续涨势，而乌克兰袭击俄罗斯炼油厂后可能出现的供应中断也支撑了油价。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 01:51:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-underpinned-by-us-inventory-data-attacks-russian-refineries-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>台湾和中国参与敏感岛屿附近的救援行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-china-dispatch-teams-join-boat-rescue-mission-near-sensitive-taiwan-2024-03-14/</link><description>在敏感的台湾海峡紧张局势加剧之际，台湾和中国派遣救援队执行罕见的联合任务，营救周四在台湾控制的金门群岛附近倾覆的船只。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 01:34:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-china-dispatch-teams-join-boat-rescue-mission-near-sensitive-taiwan-2024-03-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国官员表示，美韩防务谈判已步入正轨，但 11 月并非硬性最后期限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-south-korea-defense-talks-track-november-not-hard-deadline-us-official-2024-03-13/</link><description>拜登政府一位高级官员告诉路透社，美韩关于分担驻韩美军费用的谈判正在按计划进行，并且提前完成，但美方不一定会在 11 月美国大选之前看到一个严格的最后期限。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 23:51:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-south-korea-defense-talks-track-november-not-hard-deadline-us-official-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>随着关系改善，中国外交部长将于下周访问澳大利亚</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-foreign-minister-visit-australia-next-week-guardian-reports-2024-03-13/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·艾博内塞周四表示，中国最高外交官、外交部长王毅将于下周访问澳大利亚，这是两国关系在多年紧张局势后进一步解冻的迹象。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 23:18:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-foreign-minister-visit-australia-next-week-guardian-reports-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>由于价格下跌打击高成本矿商，中国锂热潮放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lithium-boom-slows-sagging-prices-batter-high-cost-miners-2024-03-13/</link><description>锂是电动汽车电池的关键原材料，其价格暴跌正在拖累中国的超轻金属开采，加上成本高昂的提取工艺，促使人们重新评估产量增长和新项目计划。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 23:07:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-lithium-boom-slows-sagging-prices-batter-high-cost-miners-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>保险公司友邦保险 (AIA) 2023 年新业务价值因香港销售强劲而飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/insurer-aias-2023-new-business-value-soars-strong-hong-kong-sales-2024-03-13/</link><description>周四，友邦保险集团报告称，由于受益于香港对其保险产品的强劲需求，该公司的年度新业务价值 (VONB) 增长了 33%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 22:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/insurer-aias-2023-new-business-value-soars-strong-hong-kong-sales-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>随着南海紧张局势升级，菲律宾马科斯将于下周会见布林肯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-meet-blinken-next-week-presidential-office-says-2024-03-13/</link><description>马尼拉领导人办公室周三晚间在一份声明中表示，菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯将于 3 月 19 日会见美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯，讨论合作和安全问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 22:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-meet-blinken-next-week-presidential-office-says-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>生物技术行业协会将与中国药明康德分家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/biotech-trade-association-split-with-chinas-wuxi-apptec-2024-03-13/</link><description>总部位于华盛顿的一家代表生物技术公司的全球贸易协会正在采取措施，与中国会员药明康德“分离”，根据该协会新任首席执行官周三的一封信。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 22:28:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/biotech-trade-association-split-with-chinas-wuxi-apptec-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦表示，随着中国增加出口，美国的目标是确保国内电动汽车制造商取得成功</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/yellen-says-us-moving-ensure-domestic-ev-maker-success-despite-chinas-exports-2024-03-13/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周三表示，面对中国不断增长的电动汽车出口和巨额政府补贴，总统乔·拜登的政府正在采取措施确保国内电动汽车（EV）行业的成功。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 20:28:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/yellen-says-us-moving-ensure-domestic-ev-maker-success-despite-chinas-exports-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>泽连斯基幕僚长与中国大使讨论和平前景及峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/zelenskiys-chief-staff-discusses-peace-prospects-summit-with-chinese-ambassador-2024-03-13/</link><description>乌克兰总统泽伦斯基的幕僚长周三会见了中国驻基辅大使，讨论了中国特使上周访问基辅的事宜，以及专门讨论与俄罗斯长达两年的冲突的世界峰会的筹备工作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 18:59:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/zelenskiys-chief-staff-discusses-peace-prospects-summit-with-chinese-ambassador-2024-03-13/</guid></item><item><title>麦当劳首席财务官表示海外销售将进一步疲软，中东和中国受到打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/mcdonalds-cfo-says-overseas-sales-weaken-more-middle-east-china-hit-2024-03-13/</link><description>麦当劳首席财务官伊恩·博登(Ian Borden)周三表示，受中东冲突和中国需求疲软的压力，麦当劳本季度的国际销售额将连续下降，导致其股价早盘下跌2%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:22:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/mcdonalds-cfo-says-overseas-sales-weaken-more-middle-east-china-hit-2024-03-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>